  "description": "<p><strong>IMMEDIATE ONBOARDING*</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Details:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Salary up to $3159</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Bonus up to $3500</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Fixed Deployment &amp; Shift</strong></li>\n  <li>Candidates with no experience welcomed to apply</li>\n  <li>Training Provided</li>\n  <li>All Genders Welcomed!</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Summons Issuance</li>\n  <li>Feedback Response</li>\n  <li>Parking Management</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Minimum Secondary 2</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Singaporeans only</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Class 2A/2B/2 License Required</strong></li>\n  <li>Able to commit 12-hour shift (Including Weekends and Public Holiday)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Medical, dental and insurance benefits</li>\n  <li>Staff corporate rates, discounts and passes for staff and family</li>\n  <li>High career prospect in stable environment</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested parties please feel free to send your details to <strong>8498 6788</strong> or click <strong>Apply</strong>.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Alternatively, walk in and quote “JAYE”</p>\n<p><strong>Certis Commonwealth @ 6 Commonwealth Ln, Singapore 149547</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Monday to Friday, 9am to 5pm</strong></p>\n<p>We regret that only short-listed candidates will be notified.</p>",
