    "description": "<p>Certis is a leading outsourced services partner that designs, builds and operates multi-disciplinary smart security and integrated services. Our multi-service offerings leverage our strong heritage in security, and are augmented by applied AI solutions. These solutions are part of our comprehensive technology development and systems integration capabilities that are fully cyber secure by design.</p>\n<p>At Certis, we seamlessly orchestrate security, facilities management and customer experience for greater cost efficiencies that empower your future. We are committed to building a safer, smarter, better and more sustainable business for you.</p>\n<p>As a diverse tech-led security organisation, team members enjoy job rotations within the wide Certis Group, with opportunities for continuous learning and the strengthening of skill-sets. Certis offers you a platform to shine in the operations realm and the chance to build meaningful relationships working together with like-minded colleagues.</p>\n<p>Certis is headquartered in Singapore, with an international presence that extends to Australia, Hong Kong, Macau, China and Qatar.</p>",
